author: alally
msg: Eliminated redundant LICENSE, NOTICE, DISCLAIMER files.
Maven antrun plugin now used to copy these resources from
a single location into the target/src/main/resources/META-INF
directory of each project.
UIMA-334: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/UIMA-334
